---
// PROTOTYPE — not linked from main nav. Visit /design-preview/dark-hero to view.
// Tests Claude Design's dark theme + Narukama flame hero direction with a
// simplified radial-gradient flame (full Narukama SVG with animations is
// reserved for a phase 4b port if this direction proves out).
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="zh-Hant-TW">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Design Preview · Dark Hero · 熱聲實驗室</title>
    <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;500;700&family=JetBrains+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap"
    />
    <style>
      :root {
        --dk-bg: #05080f;
        --dk-bg-soft: #0a1018;
        --dk-bg-card: #0d1422;
        --dk-bg-elev: #131c2c;
        --dk-fg-1: #f3f5f8;
        --dk-fg-2: rgba(243, 245, 248, 0.78);
        --dk-fg-3: rgba(243, 245, 248, 0.52);
        --dk-fg-4: rgba(243, 245, 248, 0.32);
        --dk-border: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        --dk-border-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.16);
        --flame-core: #ffe7a8;
        --flame-yellow: #ffba59;
        --flame-orange: #ff7a30;
        --flame-red: #e83a1a;
        --flame-deep: #7a160a;
        --font-sans:
          "Inter", "Noto Sans TC", -apple-system, "PingFang TC",
          "Microsoft JhengHei", sans-serif;
        --font-mono: "JetBrains Mono", ui-monospace, monospace;
      }
      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; }
      body {
        background: var(--dk-bg);
        color: var(--dk-fg-2);
        font-family: var(--font-sans);
        line-height: 1.6;
        -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
      }
      .container {
        max-width: 1152px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 0 24px;
      }
      @media (min-width: 768px) { .container { padding: 0 48px; } }

      /* Prototype banner */
      .proto-banner {
        background: rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.08);
        border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.18);
        color: var(--dk-fg-2);
        font-size: 13px;
        padding: 8px 0;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .proto-banner a { color: var(--flame-orange); text-decoration: underline; }
      .proto-banner code { font-family: var(--font-mono); }

      /* Header */
      .site-header {
        background: rgba(5, 8, 15, 0.85);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--dk-border);
        padding: 16px 0;
      }
      .header-inner {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: space-between;
        gap: 24px;
      }
      .brand {
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 12px;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .brand-symbol {
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        flex-shrink: 0;
      }
      .brand-symbol path:first-child { stroke: #fff; stroke-width: 2; fill: none; }
      .brand-symbol path:last-child {
        stroke: var(--flame-orange);
        stroke-width: 2;
        fill: none;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 0 4px rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.6));
      }
      .brand-zh {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: var(--dk-fg-1);
      }
      .brand-en {
        font-size: 10px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--dk-fg-3);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.1em;
        margin-top: 2px;
      }
      .nav { display: flex; gap: 24px; }
      .nav a {
        color: var(--dk-fg-2);
        text-decoration: none;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: color 150ms;
      }
      .nav a:hover { color: var(--flame-orange); }
      .nav a.is-current {
        color: var(--flame-orange);
        border-bottom: 2px solid var(--flame-orange);
        padding-bottom: 2px;
      }

      /* Hero */
      .hero { padding: 80px 0 64px; position: relative; }
      .hero-grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
        gap: 40px;
        align-items: center;
      }
      @media (min-width: 900px) {
        .hero-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; gap: 64px; }
      }

      .status-pill {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 8px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: var(--dk-fg-3);
        font-weight: 500;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-bottom: 24px;
      }
      .status-dot {
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        border-radius: 50%;
        background: var(--flame-orange);
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.7);
        animation: pulse 2s ease-in-out infinite;
      }
      @keyframes pulse {
        0%, 100% { opacity: 1; }
        50% { opacity: 0.5; }
      }

      h1.hero-title {
        font-size: 64px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.05;
        letter-spacing: -0.02em;
        color: var(--dk-fg-1);
        margin: 0;
      }
      .hero-subtitle {
        font-size: 18px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.16em;
        color: var(--flame-orange);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        margin-top: 12px;
      }
      .hero-body {
        font-size: 16px;
        color: var(--dk-fg-2);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-top: 28px;
        max-width: 30em;
      }
      .hero-actions { margin-top: 32px; display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
      .btn {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        font-size: 14px;
        font-weight: 600;
        padding: 12px 22px;
        border-radius: 4px;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: 150ms ease-out;
        cursor: pointer;
        border: 1px solid transparent;
      }
      .btn-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ff8838, #e84e15);
        color: #1a0a05;
        box-shadow:
          0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 138, 56, 0.4),
          0 8px 24px rgba(232, 78, 21, 0.25);
      }
      .btn-primary:hover {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, #ffa356, #ff6a28);
        box-shadow:
          0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 138, 56, 0.6),
          0 8px 32px rgba(232, 78, 21, 0.4);
      }
      .btn-secondary {
        background: transparent;
        color: var(--dk-fg-1);
        border-color: var(--dk-border-strong);
      }
      .btn-secondary:hover {
        border-color: var(--flame-orange);
        color: var(--flame-orange);
      }

      /* Flame visual (simplified — gradient blob, not full Narukama) */
      .flame-wrap {
        position: relative;
        min-height: 460px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      .flame-core {
        position: absolute;
        width: 320px;
        height: 460px;
        background: radial-gradient(
          ellipse at 50% 70%,
          var(--flame-core) 0%,
          var(--flame-yellow) 18%,
          var(--flame-orange) 38%,
          var(--flame-red) 62%,
          rgba(122, 22, 10, 0.4) 80%,
          transparent 100%
        );
        filter: blur(2px);
        animation: flicker 3s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
        mix-blend-mode: screen;
      }
      .flame-glow {
        position: absolute;
        width: 480px;
        height: 480px;
        background: radial-gradient(
          circle,
          rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.3) 0%,
          rgba(232, 58, 26, 0.15) 35%,
          transparent 70%
        );
        animation: glow 4s ease-in-out infinite alternate;
      }
      @keyframes flicker {
        0% { transform: scale(1) translateY(0); opacity: 0.95; }
        50% { transform: scale(1.04, 0.97) translateY(-2px); opacity: 1; }
        100% { transform: scale(0.98, 1.03) translateY(2px); opacity: 0.92; }
      }
      @keyframes glow {
        0% { transform: scale(1); opacity: 0.8; }
        100% { transform: scale(1.08); opacity: 1; }
      }
      .flame-note {
        position: absolute;
        bottom: -8px;
        font-size: 11px;
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        color: var(--dk-fg-4);
        letter-spacing: 0.06em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        text-align: center;
        width: 100%;
      }

      /* Section header */
      .section { padding: 64px 0; }
      .section-rule {
        width: 48px;
        height: 2px;
        background: var(--flame-orange);
        box-shadow: 0 0 12px rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.5);
        margin-bottom: 16px;
      }
      .eyebrow {
        font-size: 12px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--flame-orange);
        margin-bottom: 8px;
      }
      h2 {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: 600;
        line-height: 1.2;
        letter-spacing: -0.015em;
        color: var(--dk-fg-1);
        margin: 0 0 24px;
      }

      /* Card */
      .cards { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 20px; margin-top: 32px; }
      @media (min-width: 768px) { .cards { grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; } }
      .card {
        background: var(--dk-bg-card);
        border: 1px solid var(--dk-border);
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 28px;
        color: var(--dk-fg-2);
        transition: 200ms ease-out;
      }
      .card:hover {
        border-color: rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.4);
        box-shadow:
          0 0 0 1px rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.2),
          0 8px 32px rgba(255, 122, 48, 0.08);
        transform: translateY(-1px);
      }
      .card-num {
        font-family: var(--font-mono);
        font-size: 11px;
        color: var(--flame-orange);
        letter-spacing: 0.08em;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .card-title {
        font-size: 20px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--dk-fg-1);
        line-height: 1.3;
        margin: 0 0 4px;
      }
      .card-title-en {
        display: block;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 500;
        color: var(--dk-fg-3);
        margin-top: 4px;
      }
      .card-body {
        font-size: 14px;
        line-height: 1.65;
        margin-top: 12px;
      }
      .card-link {
        display: inline-block;
        margin-top: 16px;
        font-size: 13px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--dk-fg-1);
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: color 150ms;
      }
      .card:hover .card-link { color: var(--flame-orange); }

      /* Compare strip */
      .compare {
        border-top: 1px solid var(--dk-border);
        padding: 40px 0 80px;
        font-size: 13px;
        color: var(--dk-fg-3);
        text-align: center;
      }
      .compare a { color: var(--flame-orange); }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="proto-banner">
      🧪 Design preview <code>/design-preview/dark-hero</code> · not linked from
      the live site · <a href="/">回主站</a>
    </div>

    <header class="site-header">
      <div class="container header-inner">
        <a href="#" class="brand">
          <svg
            class="brand-symbol"
            viewBox="0 0 32 32"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            aria-hidden="true"
          >
            <path d="M 2 16 Q 8 8, 16 16 T 30 16" />
            <path d="M 2 22 Q 8 14, 16 22 T 30 22" />
          </svg>
          <div>
            <div class="brand-zh">熱聲實驗室</div>
            <div class="brand-en">Thermoacoustic Lab · NTUT</div>
          </div>
        </a>
        <nav class="nav">
          <a href="#" class="is-current">首頁</a>
          <a href="#">研究</a>
          <a href="#">成員</a>
          <a href="#">發表</a>
          <a href="#">計劃</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-grid">
          <div>
            <div class="status-pill">
              <span class="status-dot"></span>
              <span>正在運轉 · 24 小時無休</span>
            </div>
            <h1 class="hero-title">熱聲實驗室</h1>
            <div class="hero-subtitle">Thermoacoustic Lab</div>
            <p class="hero-body">
              本實驗室隸屬於國立臺北科技大學機械工程系，研究主題涵蓋熱聲引擎、熱聲製冷機、以及非線性熱聲現象。
            </p>
            <div class="hero-actions">
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-primary">了解研究內容</a>
              <a href="#" class="btn btn-secondary">加入實驗室</a>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flame-wrap">
            <div class="flame-glow"></div>
            <div class="flame-core"></div>
            <div class="flame-note">narukama 鳴釜 · 1568</div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container">
          <div class="section-rule"></div>
          <div class="eyebrow">Research</div>
          <h2>研究方向</h2>
          <div class="cards">
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-num">01 / 引擎</div>
              <div class="card-title">
                熱聲引擎
                <span class="card-title-en">Thermoacoustic engines</span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                濕熱蓄熱器（wet regenerator）與液柱活塞耦合之行波型熱聲引擎；汲取低溫廢熱、轉換為聲功。
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="card-link">深入了解 →</a>
            </div>
            <div class="card">
              <div class="card-num">02 / 製冷</div>
              <div class="card-title">
                熱聲製冷
                <span class="card-title-en">Thermoacoustic refrigeration</span>
              </div>
              <div class="card-body">
                以聲功泵熱、無工質環境友善之製冷機；研究阻抗匹配與系統 onset 條件。
              </div>
              <a href="#" class="card-link">深入了解 →</a>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="compare">
        <div class="container">
          這是視覺方向測試頁。原 live site light theme 仍正常運作 ——
          <a href="/">回主站</a> ·
          <a href="/publications">發表頁（已採用 Design 之 filter 樣式）</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
